# 🐞 bug report

### Affected Package
@angular/http

### Description
The beta version is not working. It shows as non-existing in npm 

## 🔬 Minimal Reproduction
run:
npm i @angular/http@8.0.0-beta.10
or:
npm i @angular/http@next

## Error
<pre><code>npm ERR! code ETARGET
npm ERR! notarget No matching version found for @angular/http@8.0.0-beta.10.
npm ERR! notarget In most cases you or one of your dependencies are requesting
npm ERR! notarget a package version that doesn't exist.

npm ERR! A complete log of this run can be found in:
npm ERR!    /.npm/_logs/2019-08-23T16_47_19_964Z-debug.log</code></pre>
